1. *Sedi* tu i nećeš se pokajati. (Stay here and you won't regret it.)
2. *Sednu* malo da se odmorimo. (Let's sit down for a bit to rest.)
3. *Sedela* sam na terasi i razmišljala. (I was sitting on the terrace and thinking.)
4. *Sednuo* je pored mene. (He sat down next to me.)
5. *Sedeli* smo u kafiću i ćaskali. (We were sitting in the café and chatting.)